column5: For those of you who weren't happy about the menu block at the upper left of the pages in the Aplitex Earth skin, We've installed a new skin called Earthbound. Basically the same colours as the Aplitex but this one seems cleaner. If you want to try it,  click on "change theme" at the bottom left of the page and choose "Earthbound"  Thanks
This is a real nice layout as well. This is  similar to the older one isn't it.? How soon we forget. lol.
I kinda got used to the new one now and find it easier on the eyes.....nice to have options though ...Cheers
Im not falling for that trick again. Im happy with what I got.

Looks great. Now if only the IP website would work properly on my BB life would be better. I barely bother checking in anymore from my phone what a pain in the butt...  edit: everytime I change to IP Mobile on my phone, the site (on my computer) goes to IP Mobile, yet my phone reverts back to the default page which is not formatted for the phone. I might have to open a second account just so I can use my phone again.
Pretty cool Roy.  Not sure which I like better. I'll try this for a bit.
LOL.. You could be Rod Castor...  I like the new skin.  and kudos Roy, this was your babay!
mucho like !!!  thanks for the extra mile effort  !
Thanks as always for your time and effort Roy. I like the Earthbound the best.   Art
Very nice Roy, no more scrolling required.
Hey Roy...  You're a good man...tells your mother !!!
